<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>AI-Driven UX Personalization</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root{
    --bg:#07111f;
    --bg2:#101d34;
    --glass:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    --border:rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    --text:#ffffff;
    --sub:#cfd8e3;
    --accent:#53d8ff;
    --accent2:#8b5cf6;
}

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;
}

html{
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bg),var(--bg2));
    color:var(--text);
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* Animated Background */

.blob{
    position:fixed;
    border-radius:50%;
    filter:blur(90px);
    z-index:-1;
    animation:float 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

.b1{
    width:350px;
    height:350px;
    background:#00d9ff55;
    top:-80px;
    left:-100px;
}

.b2{
    width:300px;
    height:300px;
    background:#8b5cf655;
    bottom:-80px;
    right:-80px;
    animation-duration:13s;
}

.b3{
    width:220px;
    height:220px;
    background:#00ff9955;
    top:50%;
    left:45%;
    animation-duration:16s;
}

@keyframes float{
    from{
        transform:translateY(0) translateX(0) scale(1);
    }
    to{
        transform:translateY(-40px) translateX(30px) scale(1.15);
    }
}

/* Navbar */

nav{
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
    backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    z-index:100;
}

nav .wrap{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:16px;
}

.logo{
    font-size:24px;
    font-weight:800;
    color:var(--accent);
}

nav ul{
    display:flex;
    gap:18px;
    list-style:none;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    transition:.3s;
}

nav a:hover{
    color:var(--accent);
}

/* Hero */

.hero{
    min-height:90vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:50px 20px;
}

.hero-content{
    max-width:900px;
    animation:fadeUp 1s;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:60px;
    line-height:1.15;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#53d8ff,#8b5cf6,#00ffa6);
    -webkit-background-clip:text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.hero p{
    color:var(--sub);
    font-size:18px;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.btns{
    margin-top:35px;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin:8px;
    padding:14px 30px;
    border-radius:50px;
    text-decoration:none;
    color:white;
    transition:.4s;
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
}

.btn:hover{
    transform:translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(83,216,255,.25);
}

/* Sections */

section{
    padding:80px 20px;
}

.title{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:38px;
    margin-bottom:50px;
}

.grid{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.card{
    background:var(--glass);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    backdrop-filter:blur(18px);
    border-radius:22px;
    padding:28px;
    transition:.4s;
    opacity:0;
    transform:translateY(40px);
}

.card.show{
    opacity:1;
    transform:translateY(0);
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow:0 20px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
}

.card h3{
    margin-bottom:15px;
    color:var(--accent);
}

.card ul{
    padding-left:18px;
}

.card li{
    margin:8px 0;
    color:var(--sub);
}

.card p{
    color:var(--sub);
    line-height:1.8;
}

/* Timeline */

.timeline{
    max-width:1100px;
    margin:auto;
}

.step{
    background:var(--glass);
    margin:18px 0;
    padding:20px;
    border-left:5px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius:15px;
    transition:.4s;
}

.step:hover{
    transform:translateX(8px);
}

/* Progress */

.bar{
    margin-top:20px;
}

.label{
    margin-bottom:6px;
}

.progress{
    height:10px;
    background:#23324b;
    border-radius:20px;
    overflow:hidden;
}

.fill{
    height:100%;
    width:0;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#53d8ff,#8b5cf6);
    animation:load 2s forwards;
}

.fill.one{width:95%;}
.fill.two{width:88%;}
.fill.three{width:90%;}
.fill.four{width:85%;}

@keyframes load{
    from{width:0;}
}

/* Footer */

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:35px;
    color:#b7c5d9;
}

/* Animations */

@keyframes fadeUp{
    from{
        opacity:0;
        transform:translateY(40px);
    }
    to{
        opacity:1;
        transform:translateY(0);
    }
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero h1{
    font-size:40px;
}

.title{
    font-size:30px;
}

}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="blob b1"></div>
<div class="blob b2"></div>
<div class="blob b3"></div>

<nav>
<div class="wrap">
<div class="logo">AI UX</div>

<ul>
<li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
<li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
<li><a href="#workflow">Workflow</a></li>
<li><a href="#future">Future</a></li>
</ul>

</div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-content">

<h1>AI-Driven UX Personalization</h1>

<p>
Artificial Intelligence transforms digital experiences by learning user
behavior and automatically delivering customized interfaces, content,
recommendations, and interactions for every individual.
</p>

<div class="btns">
<a href="#about" class="btn">Explore</a>
<a href="#future" class="btn">Future Scope</a>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="about">

<h2 class="title">What is AI-Driven UX Personalization?</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>📖 Definition</h3>
<p>
AI-powered personalization adapts websites and applications based on user
preferences, browsing patterns, and interaction history to create smarter
digital experiences.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>🎯 Goal</h3>
<p>
Deliver the right content to the right user at the right time while improving
engagement, satisfaction, and usability.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>💡 Technologies</h3>
<ul>
<li>Machine Learning</li>
<li>Deep Learning</li>
<li>Natural Language Processing</li>
<li>Recommendation Systems</li>
<li>Predictive Analytics</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="features">

<h2 class="title">Key Features</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>🤖 Smart Recommendations</h3>
<p>Suggests products, videos, or articles based on user interests.</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>🔍 Intelligent Search</h3>
<p>Predicts queries and improves search accuracy using AI.</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>📊 Behavior Analysis</h3>
<p>Analyzes clicks, scrolling, and usage patterns for personalization.</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>🎨 Adaptive Interface</h3>
<p>Changes layouts and themes according to user preferences.</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>💬 AI Assistants</h3>
<p>Provides instant support through conversational chatbots.</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>⚡ Real-Time Updates</h3>
<p>Continuously improves recommendations using live interactions.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="workflow">

<h2 class="title">AI Personalization Workflow</h2>

<div class="timeline">

<div class="step">
<h3>1️⃣ Data Collection</h3>
<p>Gather browsing history, preferences, clicks, and interactions.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>2️⃣ AI Processing</h3>
<p>Machine learning models identify trends and user patterns.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>3️⃣ Prediction</h3>
<p>The system predicts future interests and likely actions.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>4️⃣ Personalization</h3>
<p>Dynamic content and interfaces are generated for each user.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section>

<h2 class="title">Performance Impact</h2>

<div style="max-width:900px;margin:auto;">

<div class="bar">
<div class="label">User Satisfaction</div>
<div class="progress">
<div class="fill one"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="bar">
<div class="label">Customer Engagement</div>
<div class="progress">
<div class="fill two"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="bar">
<div class="label">Conversion Rate</div>
<div class="progress">
<div class="fill three"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="bar">
<div class="label">Retention</div>
<div class="progress">
<div class="fill four"></div>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="future">

<h2 class="title">Future Scope</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>🌐 Hyper Personalization</h3>
<p>Highly customized digital experiences powered by advanced AI models.</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>😊 Emotion Recognition</h3>
<p>Interfaces adapting based on facial expressions and emotions.</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>🥽 AR & VR</h3>
<p>Immersive personalized virtual environments for users.</p>
</div>

<div class="card reveal">
<h3>🔒 Privacy-Aware AI</h3>
<p>Smarter personalization while protecting user data securely.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

<h3>AI-Driven UX Personalization</h3>

<p>
 Project • Glassmorphism • Responsive • Animated 
</p>

</footer>

<script>
const cards=document.querySelectorAll(".reveal");

function reveal(){
cards.forEach(card=>{
const top=card.getBoundingClientRect().top;
if(top<window.innerHeight-80){
card.classList.add("show");
}
});
}

window.addEventListener("scroll",reveal);
reveal();
</script>

</body>
</html>
